name: Fire Bow
notes: Arrow lasts 55 frames minimum (if it does not hit ground), 13 frames startup and 25 frames endlag upon release

name: Boomerang
notes: 20 frames to catch the boomerang.

name: Bomb
notes: bomb pulled out on frame 16. able to start throwing on frame 40. bomb has multipule hitboxes, unknown how much each does (damage listed assumes all hits land)

name: Down Smash
notes: front hit frames 9-11, does 13% or 7% damage. back hit frames 21-23, does 12% or 6% damage

name: Forward Air
notes: first hit frames 14-16, does 12%, 11%, or 9% damage. Second hit frames 17-33, does 8%, 7%, or 5% damage with 5 frames shield stun

name: Spin Attack
notes: Hits 8-43 loop for 1% damage, final hit on frame 44 for 3% damage

name: Rapid Jabs
notes: Separate 7 frame startup animation

name: Spin Attack (Air)
notes: x amount of 1% hitboxes followed by 3% hitbox

name: Grab
notes: Close grab is frame 11-13, hook is frame 11-14.

name: Dashgrab
notes: Close grab is frame 14-15, hook is frame 14-17.
